{"tid":1512251,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[戰術討論] 我哋究竟輸乜？輸無大台！","createTime":"2019-08-27T21:04:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T16:19:59.000Z","uid":245968,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c8e5fb6fce54cf07ade1779d067f2c17620f8e68","tid":1512251,"uid":245968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T21:04:19.000Z","msg":"我係標題黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我講嘅大台係指好似狗嘅team work<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QcT8TdG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQcT8TdG.png&h=1ee2d6f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n畫得好撚柒唔好介意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上面係狗，下面係我哋<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">速龍</span> [black]防暴牆[/black] <span style=\"color: green;\">tg,gun</span> <span style=\"color: gold;\">leader</span> <span style=\"color: blue;\">救人小隊</span><br />\n有打開GTA都知狗好多時都係咁<br />\n正常咁嘅陣容人數多就自動取勝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但當然係講緊佢哋未開槍嘅時候<br />\nTg出可以學佢哋咁成班一步一步後退<br />\n但一定要分隊分組，同每組最少有一個leader去觀察<br />\n<br />\n唔知各位手足覺得可唔可取<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ab3ab32436a710af067aec8fafdf5c669b66634","tid":1512251,"uid":245968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T21:12:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4203dcf11c080c4e4db2ab09f3fcbbcc69052c91","tid":1512251,"uid":245968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T21:35:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 